title: 381. Andy, Linda Catalina & DJ CTI: Putin: "Not A Bluff," Atlanta Fed Announces Negative 3rd Quarter & Man Ran Down Teen He Thought Was Republican Extremist
itunes:title: 381. Andy, Linda Catalina & DJ CTI: Putin: "Not A Bluff," Atlanta Fed Announces Negative 3rd Quarter & Man Ran Down Teen He Thought Was Republican Extremist
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ are joined in the studio by entrepreneur & "Mostly Peaceful Latinas" podcast host Linda Catalina. They discuss Vladimir Putin doubling down on the threat of his nuclear weapons to the West as not a bluff, the Atlanta Fed announcing a negative 3rd quarter in the market, and a man who ran down and killed a teen he thought was a Republican extremist.
